==English==

=== Proper noun ===

#An [[Archeology|archeological]] term that designates the level of [[culture]] in which man used [[iron]] and the [[technology]] of iron production. Estimated to have begun in [[Europe]] about 1100 BCE.
#Any dark or grim era, characteristic of malice, oppression, war, poverty, suffering, etc. Opposite of [[golden age]].
#a time of poor progress or controversy in a particular field

